# SSH Listening Port
Port 2222

# Authentication Settings
PermitRootLogin no
PasswordAuthentication no
PubkeyAuthentication yes

# User restrictions
AllowUsers itadmin

# Disable GUI forwarding
X11Forwarding no

# Loggin and security
LogLevel VERBOSE
ClientAliveInterval 300
ClientAliveCountMax 2

# Default settings (keep)
UsePAM yes
PrintMotd no
AcceptEnv LANG LC_*
Subsystem sftp /usr/lib/openssh/sftp-server


